      "title": "The trade union movement was abandoned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Union of Railway Station Principals has announced that the union strike that was to be carried out by the railway station principals has been abandoned.",
        "It is to be noted that the protest against the revision of train fare was canceled yesterday (23) at 6 pm. (a)"
